{"tid":1251052,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"80年尾至90年中既香港影視女星，你認得同最鍾意邊個？","createTime":"2019-06-22T10:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T16:22:04.000Z","uid":232077,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b0283ae1233705e703283ab4db48b81b6228f375","tid":1251052,"uid":232077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T10:45:29.000Z","msg":"娛樂台post過一次，但班友淨係識吹奏大陸日韓妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔講好多，去片<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NARtLSyG4Vk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNARtLSyG4Vk&d=ahpQ5aMQEo4h8Mt%2B3j6t3gEDdXZq%2B7ycbDpBQOFx8Mg%3D&h=e74c4baf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NARtLSyG4Vk</a><br />\n<br />\n睇過條越南仔剪輯先知咩叫靚同有氣質<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家班新一代根本冇得比，本身唔靚仲要整容，整完都係唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨係港姐質素，90年代初果幾個已經高質到證明港女先係世界最靚既人種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有好多老左唔靚，但依家走去睇返後生時期，一Ｄ都唔輸蝕班新一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最驚喜係睇到後生既劉玉翠，又幾可愛，唔知因咩事變左做醜婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果畀你揀一個就係女友，老婆，SP等，你會點揀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我就係<br />\n老婆：關詠荷<br />\n女友：周慧敏<br />\nSP：邱淑貞<br />\n表姐：張可頤<br />\n表妹：李嘉欣"},{"pid":"92c1cfd47257564ff17e1d91e95e21722b168119","tid":1251052,"uid":186152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T11:07:01.000Z","msg":"全部做SP"},{"pid":"c855b8eba6a7300ef209a9d2095c5306f22730e1","tid":1251052,"uid":157023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T11:33:20.000Z","msg":"嘩好靚呀真係<br />\n<br />\n個人最喜歡邱淑貞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df7ad37694d37534d0807ada522dda7ea404013","tid":1251052,"uid":6697